{"tid":1277281,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"勇士71試完後，你哋明白嗎？","createTime":"2019-07-02T06:57:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T07:20:54.000Z","uid":61396,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"fc39d6355530ef04d921506454fa38cc1beb233e","tid":1277281,"uid":61396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T06:57:06.000Z","msg":"寫歷史論文時<br />\n阿旺事件時 幾個有盾兵仔<br />\n就可以防一堆石頭<br />\n<br />\n比你入立立 係有心放水<br />\n有借口後殺光你哋<br />\n用文宣 或想直接打死你哋<br />\n只係估不到你們會走<br />\n<br />\n兵仔用完即棄<br />\n對大佬無影響<br />\n何妖 中可以拿光環話你哋暴力<br />\n<br />\n歷史話比你哋知<br />\n和李飛 係聚合眾人<br />\n用最簡單 成本最低的方法<br />\n打擊敵人（選舉）<br />\n<br />\n而勇士們<br />\n唔好再打兵仔 兵仔5000以上<br />\n大佬只得幾十人<br />\n大佬先係最仆街<br />\n笑笑口 要勇士上庭的人<br />\n要想聰明的方法<br />\n<br />\n勇者要智慧<br />\n大家要想清楚 <br />\n阻礙他們大佬的方法"},{"pid":"d1fea8a321dbbc4db8a067fb82ef36486c9d73a4","tid":1277281,"uid":205339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T07:02:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"680022271a366043ad676f4f60e94b70ae620052","tid":1277281,"uid":270394,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T07:03:44.000Z","msg":"點解九唔搭八。。&hellip;係咪得我睇唔明？"},{"pid":"25b0d6ed92ca0b0d637fa948656a786c04b2082e","tid":1277281,"uid":192997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"680022271a366043ad676f4f60e94b70ae620052","tid":1277281,"uid":270394,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T07:03:44.000Z","msg":"點解九唔搭八。。&hellip;係咪得我睇唔明？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T07:04:22.000Z","msg":"你不是自己一個"},{"pid":"96d3a958867f24c361a8abcd2c9f967be79cbe7f","tid":1277281,"uid":178470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T07:05:02.000Z","msg":"Translation error"},{"pid":"05fe2ff89b4b07fd49a2117b5a299b0f75bc1b1d","tid":1277281,"uid":260161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T07:05:42.000Z","msg":"1999<br />\n讀好書先開Post啦"},{"pid":"5283598012f0a5b290b1eebd1927